com.tedros.fxapi.process

Class TEntityProcess<E extends ITEntity>

  • java.lang.Object
    • javafx.concurrent.Service<V>
      • com.tedros.fxapi.process.TProcess<java.util.List<TResult<E>>>
        • com.tedros.fxapi.process.TEntityProcess<E>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ITProcess<java.util.List<TResult<E>>>, javafx.concurrent.Worker<java.util.List<TResult<E>>>, javafx.event.EventTarget
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    TDisabledCrudProcess, TPessoaProcess, TProfileProcess, TUserProcess

    public abstract class TEntityProcess<E extends ITEntity>
extends TProcess<java.util.List<TResult<E>>>
    Process with basic CRUD tasks.
 
 Two application server types can be used, Apache TomEE and JBOSS EAP / WildFly.
 The application server endpoint can be configured at remote-config.properties
 located at ..\.tedros\CONF in the USER folder.
    Author:
    Davis Gordon
